    FROM "Books" AS b
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Authors" AS a ON t."AuthorId" = a."Id"

LEFT JOIN "Languages" AS l ON t."LanguageId" = l."Id"
